/** * Driver method, for testing standalone. * 
   * java -Dtests.profile.count=5 buildSrc/src/main/java/org/apache/lucene/gradle/ProfileResults.java \
   *   ./lucene/core/build/tmp/tests-cwd/somefile.jfr ...
   *
*/ public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException { printReport(Arrays.asList(args), System.getProperty(MODE_KEY, MODE_DEFAULT), Integer.parseInt(System.getProperty(STACKSIZE_KEY, STACKSIZE_DEFAULT)), Integer.parseInt(System.getProperty(COUNT_KEY, COUNT_DEFAULT)), Boolean.parseBoolean(System.getProperty(LINENUMBERS_KEY, LINENUMBERS_DEFAULT))); }
